eventHighlights.title: Relay for Life
eventHighlights.description: It was a huge success, thanks to our amazing participants and generous donors! Together, we raised an impressive $8,433 placing us second in the community group category!

eventHighlights.title: Volunteers Day
eventHighlights.description:
The biggest day of the year for us! There were opportunities like Elder Care Volunteering where students connected with residents through music, arts, and crafts!
 Other students volunteered for the Takapuna Beach Clean Up, helping to preserve the beautiful beach!

eventHighlights.title: Blind Low Vision
eventHighlights.description: All the volunteers helped Blind Low Vision NZ to clean all their donation buckets! The organisation helps to train guide dogs who support Kiwis who are blind, deafblind, or have low vision.

eventHighlights.title: Pub Quiz
eventHighlights.description: A great night filled with some very interesting questions and free food!
